properties.Name: DunBradstreetCreditRiskCategory
properties.Description:
A categorization of the risk to the supplier by extending credit to the Party.

Examples from Dun & Bradstreet rating service:

Credit Risk Category 1 (HIGH) - Relatively low risk 
Credit Risk Category 2 (GOOD) - Moderate credit risk
Credit Risk Category 3 (FAIR) - Poor credit risk
Credit Risk Category 4 (LIMITED) - Information unavailable

Columns.Name: DunBradstreetCreditRiskCategoryId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Dun Bradstreet Credit Risk Category.

Columns.Name: DunBradstreetCreditRiskCategoryName
Columns.Description: The name of the Dun Bradstreet Credit Risk Category.

Columns.Name: DunBradstreetCreditRiskCategoryDescription
Columns.Description: The description of the Dun Bradstreet Credit Risk Category.
